# Example crontab for running the car deal bot.
#
# Install with: crontab -e   (then paste one of the lines below)
# View current: crontab -l
#
# Adjust the path to wherever you put this project.

# --- Every 15 minutes (recommended) -----------------------------------------
*/15 * * * * cd /home/YOU/car-deal-bot && /usr/bin/python3 main.py >> bot.log 2>&1

# --- Every 10 minutes (more aggressive — watch for rate limits) -------------
# */10 * * * * cd /home/YOU/car-deal-bot && /usr/bin/python3 main.py >> bot.log 2>&1

# --- Once an hour (casual) --------------------------------------------------
# 0 * * * * cd /home/YOU/car-deal-bot && /usr/bin/python3 main.py >> bot.log 2>&1
